A way for enduser to input data to the database

done through WT-Forms
With CSRF protection
    WTForms offers protection through 
        <!-- form.hidden_tag() -->
        on any html page which performs POST
        <!-- SECRET_KEY -->
        app.config["SECRET_KEY"] = "literally anystring"
        best to hide ^ through a variable
        app.confid["SECRET_KEY"] = os.getenv('SECRET_KEY')

Forms: Uses FlaskForm class
    Class FromName(FLaskForm):
        name = Stringfield("Name")
        submit = SubmitField("Submit") - will be in forms.py

Different form fields 
    StringField
    IntegerField
    BooleanField
    DateField
    DateTimefield
    DecimalFireld
    SubmitField
    SelectField

